1010
00:52:26,419 --> 00:52:27,477
Did you see that, Nana?

1011
00:52:27,520 --> 00:52:31,286
People in big cities like Mumbai
are talking about our village.

1012
00:52:31,391 --> 00:52:34,383
Didn't l tell you our village
will be very famous one day?

1013
00:52:34,427 --> 00:52:35,485
Subhedar.
- Yes?

1014
00:52:35,562 --> 00:52:36,859
Nana is over here, not there.

1015
00:52:37,697 --> 00:52:39,688
Dhuliya, here l come!

1016
00:52:39,766 --> 00:52:41,324
Lights! Camera! Action!

1017
00:52:41,468 --> 00:52:43,527
What a nice place. We'll
take the first shot here.

1018
00:52:44,971 --> 00:52:46,529
Boss, camera.

1019
00:52:46,606 --> 00:52:47,698
That's more like it.

1020
00:52:47,774 --> 00:52:50,334
This isn't a small film. lt's a
big film. Go bring a bigger camera.

1021
00:52:50,410 --> 00:52:51,934
Boss, where do l keep this?
