Aatish's Oscar to Aamir.

1215
01:01:49,048 --> 01:01:50,982
No. No. l don't want
to hear the story.

1216
01:01:51,050 --> 01:01:52,347
l just need the Oscar.

1217
01:01:52,418 --> 01:01:55,854
l will narrate the story to you,
Mr. Aatish. l insist, darling.

1218
01:01:56,756 --> 01:02:01,386
The story revolves
around a great person..

1219
01:02:01,560 --> 01:02:06,259
