1220
01:02:08,601 --> 01:02:10,296
But the story..

1221
01:02:11,637 --> 01:02:13,332
What is the story?

1222
01:02:15,541 --> 01:02:17,532
Tees Maar Khan is a revolutionary..

1223
01:02:17,576 --> 01:02:21,535
..who is involved in the greatest
revolt against the British rule.

1224
01:02:21,781 --> 01:02:24,716
He robs diamonds, pearls
and jewellery worth billions.

1225
01:02:25,484 --> 01:02:27,475
An astonishing plan.

1226
01:02:27,987 --> 01:02:30,455
Nail-biting suspense.

1227
01:02:31,290 --> 01:02:33,588
What?
- What is that plan?

1228
01:02:33,793 --> 01:02:35,886
''Tees Maar Khan.''

1229
01:02:36,662 --> 01:02:38,061
That's the suspense.

1230
01:02:38,531 --> 01:02:40,328
l like the story.
l'm doing the film.

1231
01:02:41,534 --> 01:02:42,899
That's what l expected from you.

1232
01:02:43,502 --> 01:02:45,470
Tell Aamir he's out.

1233
01:02:46,505 --> 01:02:48,336
Sorry, Aamir. You're out.
- Oh, no.

1234
01:02:48,541 --> 01:02:51,567
But what about his fees? Money?

1235
01:02:52,812 --> 01:02:54,006
Aatish, put your hand on
your heart..

1236
01:02:54,080 --> 01:02:55,911
..and tell me whether you
want money or the Oscar.

1237
01:02:55,981 --> 01:02:57,312
Oscar.

1238
01:02:57,850 --> 01:02:59,044
Day ho!

1239
01:03:01,654 --> 01:03:03,884
Manoj Day.
- Day ho!

1240
01:03:04,256 --> 01:03:06,349
- Day ho!
- Day ho!

