Attack him. Do you have a gun?

2079
01:47:34,297 --> 01:47:37,266
Yes. The latest piece, sir.
Smith & Wesson.

2080
01:47:37,901 --> 01:47:40,597
Excellent! Now remove
all the bullets from it.

2081
