Just do as l tell you to do.

2088
01:47:54,884 --> 01:47:57,944
Throw away the bullets
and arrest Tees Maar Khan.

2089
01:47:58,321 --> 01:47:59,754
Okay, sir.
- Remove them.

2090
01:48:01,558 --> 01:48:02,616
Throw them away.

2091
01:48:04,194 --> 01:48:05,286
Hands up!

2092
01:48:05,895 --> 01:48:08,329
Sir, we've arrested Tees Maar Khan.

2093
01:48:08,698 --> 01:48:10,063
Swear on me.
- l swear on you.

2094
01:48:10,634 --> 01:48:12,033
Surprise!

2095
01:48:16,172 --> 01:48:20,802
Saving the honour of a harlot
and imprisoning Tees Maar Khan.

2096
01:48:20,977 --> 01:48:22,342
Both are futile.

2097
01:48:30,153 --> 01:48:31,711
Hurry up. Hurry up!

2098
01:48:31,788 --> 01:48:36,122
Get in. Get in. Old woman,
get in the car.

2099
01:48:37,661 --> 01:48:39,856
Villagers, keep singing.

