01:48:40,030 --> 01:48:42,225
l've placed cameras all around you.

2101
01:48:42,299 --> 01:48:46,565
Smile! Sing! Aatish, sing. Sing.

2102
01:48:46,636 --> 01:48:47,864
Okay.

2103
01:49:10,960 --> 01:49:12,086
Come on, quickly.

2104
01:49:12,796 --> 01:49:14,127
lsn't Aatish coming with us?

2105
01:49:14,164 --> 01:49:15,722
He's gone to get
a suit made for the Oscars.

2106
01:49:16,666 --> 01:49:18,065
Even l wanted a dress.

2107
01:49:18,134 --> 01:49:20,837
l want to watch the film shooting,
Tabrez. - Yes, l'll show you.

2108
01:49:20,837 --> 01:49:21,997
lt's such a beautiful place.
Show me the film shoot.

2109
01:49:22,172 --> 01:49:23,799
Do one thing. Take them both.

2110
01:49:23,840 --> 01:49:24,898
Take them to Mumbai.

2111
01:49:24,974 --> 01:49:26,566
Mother, let's go.

2112
01:49:26,643 --> 01:49:27,871
Stop doing that.

2113
01:49:27,944 --> 01:49:30,071
Gets your legs inside quickly.

2114
01:49:30,246 --> 01:49:32,146
Take them to Mumbai.
Take them away.

2115
01:49:32,882 --> 01:49:34,144
When is the next shot?

2116
01:49:34,217 --> 01:49:35,684
Yes, next year.

2117
01:49:37,120 --> 01:49:38,781
Give me the keys to
the trunk. Quickly.

2118
01:49:38,922 --> 01:49:40,787
Why? Do you want to deposit
the treasure in the bank?

2119
01:49:41,124 --> 01:49:42,216
No.

2120
01:49:42,559 --> 01:49:43,992
l had promised myself..

2121
01:49:44,761 --> 01:49:46,854
..that l'd leave some
valuables for the villagers.

2122
01:49:48,264 --> 01:49:50,664
He's large hearted.

2123
01:49:50,734 --> 01:49:51,996
Give me five.

2124
01:49:53,269 --> 01:49:54,998
Are you out of your mind?

2125
01:49:55,305 --> 01:49:56,897
l'm not asking for
your permission. Okay?

2126
01:49:57,107 --> 01:49:58,665
l'm telling you about my decision.

2127
01:49:58,742 --> 01:50:00,642
Besides, we're
giving it from our share.

2128
01:50:00,710 --> 01:50:01,802
You have nothing to do with it.

2129
01:50:01,845 --> 01:50:03,278
Come on. Remove the
keys from your pocket.

2130
01:50:04,714 --> 01:50:05,772
Come on.

2131
01:50:06,716 --> 01:50:07,774
Share?

2132
01:50:24,167 --> 01:50:25,725
Come on!

2133
01:50:27,704 --> 01:50:28,898
Move!

2134
01:50:33,143 --> 01:50:35,236
Being an inspector,
you're helping a criminal.

2135
01:50:36,045 --> 01:50:38,775
l'm Commissioner Khadak Singh.

2136
01:50:39,315 --> 01:50:42,910
The one who you've helped
rob 'Bharat ka Khazana'..

2137
01:50:42,986 --> 01:50:46,513
..is the wanted
criminal Tees Maar Khan.

2138
01:50:46,589 --> 01:50:47,817
Yes.
- What?

2139
01:50:48,158 --> 01:50:50,251
Yes. l knew it..

2140
01:50:51,227 --> 01:50:53,252
Sir, how did this happen?
l didn't get it.

2141
01:50:53,530 --> 01:50:54,827
Darn it. Didn't even realise it.

2142
01:50:58,301 --> 01:51:00,269
Tees Maar Khan!

2143
01:51:00,770 --> 01:51:02,032
Quickly. Quickly.

2144
01:51:02,205 --> 01:51:03,297
Listen. Listen.

2145
01:51:03,706 --> 01:51:05,298
Let's put this in the bank.

2146
01:51:05,608 --> 01:51:07,166
You take care of that two-in-one.
- Okay, boss.

2147
01:51:07,243 --> 01:51:08,608
Quickly. Quickly. Go on.

2148
01:51:11,214 --> 01:51:13,011
Boss, looks like he's dead.
Should l check him?

2149
01:51:13,082 --> 01:51:15,050
ls he your uncle?
- No, boss.

2150
01:51:22,959 --> 01:51:24,756
Hello? Tees Maar Khan?

2151
01:51:24,861 --> 01:51:27,159
You need one more box?
Will send it right away.

2152
01:51:27,764 --> 01:51:29,231
Boss has asked for another box.

2153
01:51:29,299 --> 01:51:30,857
Okay. Okay.

2154
01:51:38,808 --> 01:51:41,641
Boss, the Johri brothers
have escaped.

2155
01:51:43,713 --> 01:51:45,738
Stop!

2156
01:51:48,785 --> 01:51:50,514
Why did you let them go?

2157
01:51:50,587 --> 01:51:51,986
They said you asked me to.

2158
01:51:52,055 --> 01:51:53,716
When did l tell him?
- Hands up.

2159
01:51:53,857 --> 01:51:55,017
Let it go.

2160
01:51:55,258 --> 01:51:57,749
Hands up, Tees Maar Khan.

2161
01:52:00,730 --> 01:52:02,095
Speak now.

2162
01:52:06,669 --> 01:52:08,534
This poor guy is still
in character.

2163
01:52:08,605 --> 01:52:09,867
The film shooting is over.

2164
01:52:09,939 --> 01:52:13,534
Your game is up, Tees Maar Khan.

2165
01:52:14,010 --> 01:52:18,242
Look, there's no
enmity between us.

2166
01:52:18,681 --> 01:52:20,046
You're a good actor.

2167
01:52:20,884 --> 01:52:22,875
Come to Mumbai.
l'll introduce you to Yash Chopra.

2168
01:52:23,086 --> 01:52:24,144
He's our uncle.

2169
01:52:24,220 --> 01:52:25,812
Enough film shooting.

2170
01:52:25,989 --> 01:52:27,547
Now surrender
yourself to me quietly.

2171
01:52:27,624 --> 01:52:29,854
Dharindar.. - lt's not Dharindar.
lt's Dhurinder.

2172
01:52:30,126 --> 01:52:32,094
