01:52:45,575 --> 01:52:48,703
Tees Maar Khan,
you're under arrest.

2177
01:52:53,983 --> 01:52:55,712
l'll deal with you back
in Mumbai Doordarshan.

2178
01:52:56,019 --> 01:52:57,111
Order! Order!

2179
01:52:57,887 --> 01:52:59,650
Present the accused in court.

2180
01:53:00,957 --> 01:53:02,151
Stand up.

2181
01:53:02,926 --> 01:53:04,826
All these?
All these are the accused?

2182
