Yes, My Lord. The whole village
is filled with criminals.

2183
01:53:11,901 --> 01:53:13,960
No! No!
- No, Your Honour!

2184
01:53:14,037 --> 01:53:15,766
Order! Order! Silence.

2185
01:53:15,838 --> 01:53:17,635
Speak one by one.

2186
01:53:17,707 --> 01:53:19,607
The whole village carried
out the robbery together.

2187
01:53:19,676 --> 01:53:21,576
They deserve the harshest
of punishments, My Lord.

2188
01:53:21,644 --> 01:53:23,168
No! No!

2189
01:53:23,680 --> 01:53:26,080
Quiet. Quiet.

2190
01:53:31,287 --> 01:53:32,584
Who are you, brother?

2191
01:53:32,655 --> 01:53:35,818
lnternational film
director Manoj Day Ramalan.

2192
01:53:35,992 --> 01:53:38,859
l had ordered phony
treasures for my film shoot.

2193
01:53:38,928 --> 01:53:42,557
But sir, some scoundrel
sent genuine treasures.

2194
01:53:42,632 --> 01:53:45,829
And l suspect it is Steven.

2195
01:53:45,902 --> 01:53:47,164
Steven?
- Spielberg.

2196
01:53:47,236 --> 01:53:48,828
He's a liar, Your Honour.

2197
01:53:49,238 --> 01:53:52,036
Firstly, he's
himself a wanted criminal.

2198
01:53:52,709 --> 01:53:55,837
Secondly, he has
been to prison 11 times.

2199
01:53:55,912 --> 01:53:57,812
And he's escaped
from prison 25 times.

2200
01:53:57,880 --> 01:54:00,212
How dare you! l'll
sue you for defamation.

2201
01:54:00,283 --> 01:54:02,615
Get through this case first.
- Sorry, sir.

2202
01:54:02,785 --> 01:54:07,154
To prove his true identity,
l'd like to present two witnesses.

2203
01:54:07,757 --> 01:54:11,659
Special Officers,
Chatterjee and Mukherjee.

2204
01:54:12,595 --> 01:54:13,755
Go ahead.

2205
01:54:14,230 --> 01:54:16,721
Your Honour,
we personally arrested him in Paris.

2206
01:54:16,799 --> 01:54:18,858
But he tricked us and escaped.

2207
01:54:19,102 --> 01:54:21,730
Yes, Your Honour. This is
the international criminal..

2208
01:54:21,804 --> 01:54:25,604
..Tabrez Mirza Khan
alias Tees Maar Khan.

2209
01:54:25,808 --> 01:54:28,368
No. No.

2210
01:54:33,916 --> 01:54:36,316
Your Honour, wait. Wait.

2211
01:54:36,986 --> 01:54:39,887
He's not a criminal. He's a godsend.

2212
01:54:41,858 --> 01:54:47,091
The director left this share of
the treasure at the bank for us.

2213
01:54:47,163 --> 01:54:48,721
For us villagers.

2214
01:54:49,699 --> 01:54:52,827
He's large hearted.

2215
01:54:54,103 --> 01:54:57,971
Your Honour, because of
him l got my son back.

2216
01:54:58,041 --> 01:54:59,565
He can't be a criminal.

2217
01:54:59,642 --> 01:55:00,802
Yes! He can't be.

2218
01:55:00,843 --> 01:55:03,971
lf he's Tees Maar Khan,
then what do we care?

2219
01:55:04,147 --> 01:55:06,672
But he's always thought
about the welfare of the village.

2220
01:55:06,816 --> 01:55:07,942
Yes. Yes. He thought
about our welfare.

2221
01:55:08,017 --> 01:55:11,316
My son might be a criminal,
but he's pure at heart.

2222
01:55:11,587 --> 01:55:12,952
And also cute.

2223
01:55:13,856 --> 01:55:14,982
Silence! Silence!

2224
01:55:15,058 --> 01:55:18,050
Your Honour,
had he been a criminal..

2225
01:55:18,127 --> 01:55:20,652
..he wouldn't have left the
treasure for the villagers.

2226
01:55:20,730 --> 01:55:22,129
You bet.

2227
01:55:22,198 --> 01:55:23,256
Yes. Yes.

2228
01:55:23,332 --> 01:55:26,324
He might've shown me false
dreams about the Oscars..

2229
01:55:26,602 --> 01:55:31,767
..but he has awakened the
artist in me, Your Honour.

2230
01:55:31,874 --> 01:55:34,968
lf he's a criminal, then so am l.

2231
01:55:35,078 --> 01:55:37,069
Punish me as well.
Punish me as well.

2232
01:55:37,146 --> 01:55:38,636
Punish us as well.

2233
01:55:38,715 --> 01:55:39,773
Punish us as well!

2234
01:55:39,849 --> 01:55:41,043
Quiet. Quiet. Silence. Silence.

2235
01:55:41,117 --> 01:55:42,641
Order! Order!

2236
01:55:42,719 --> 01:55:44,243
Brother, what now?

2237
01:55:44,320 --> 01:55:45,617
What do l know, brother?

2238
01:55:45,755 --> 01:55:47,655
Silence! Quiet! Quiet!

2239
01:55:47,724 --> 01:55:48,884
Punish us as well!

2240
01:55:48,958 --> 01:55:51,984
Did you see that, My Lord?
They're all criminals.

2241
01:55:52,261 --> 01:55:53,626
Punish them.

2242
01:55:53,696 --> 01:55:55,220
l will. l'll surely punish them.

2243
01:55:55,598 --> 01:55:58,066
Quiet! Let me speak.

2244
01:55:58,868 --> 01:56:02,065
On account of all the
evidence and testimonies..

2245
01:56:02,138 --> 01:56:04,299
..this court declares
Tees Maar Khan..

2246
01:56:04,574 --> 01:56:07,702
..and the villagers of
Dhuliya guilty.

2247
01:56:07,777 --> 01:56:11,235
No! No. - What are you saying,
Your Honour?

2248
01:56:11,314 --> 01:56:13,782
What nonsense is this?
- This is not possible.

2249
01:56:15,284 --> 01:56:16,717
Just a minute, Your Honour.

2250
01:56:17,687 --> 01:56:19,018
What now?

2251
01:56:19,088 --> 01:56:20,817
All these people are innocent.

2252
01:56:21,624 --> 01:56:22,921
l'm the only culprit.

2253
01:56:23,826 --> 01:56:27,728
ln fact, l deceived these
decent people and have misled them.

2254
01:56:29,265 --> 01:56:31,859
They didn't even know that a
robbery was about to take place.

2255
01:56:32,368 --> 01:56:33,858
So Your Honour, l request you..

2256
01:56:33,936 --> 01:56:35,870
..that only l should be punished.

2257
01:56:35,938 --> 01:56:38,839
Okay, only you will be punished.

2258
01:56:39,275 --> 01:56:42,267
This court announces 60
years imprisonment for you.

2259
01:56:42,745 --> 01:56:43,939
No!

2260
01:56:44,013 --> 01:56:45,810
